      • addResolutionCalculator

        public void addResolutionCalculator(ResolutionCalculator calc)
        Causes the MouseListener to use a ResolutionCalculator to adjust mouse locations. Note: The x and y coordinates in the child class' handling functions will not be affected by the ResolutionCalculator, and will have to adjust any X and Y coordinates accordingly.
        Parameters:
        calc - The ResolutionCalculator to add.
